title: Neff Ninja Isaiah Johnson Goes Mad
description: At Neff we sponsor some of the best pro skaters in the world. Not only do we sponsor the best pro's but we look for the best up-and-coming skaters and stand back as our minds are blown. Check out this little piece shot and edited by Isaiah Johnson and friends. See what the skate team has been up to on our website: https://www.neffheadwear.com/skate
